Break down,Break down

51
00:03:32,921 --> 00:03:37,550
Let the voice of
love take you higher

52
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:44,140
聚集的力量 连时光都能超越

53
00:03:45,516 --> 00:03:50,355
Let the joy of love
give you an answer

54
00:03:50,438 --> 00:03:56,861
连离别的时候 都用不灭的意志

55
